HEADWORD: Bewit
<hw>Bew"it</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. OF.
<ets>buie</ets> bond, chain, fr. L. <ets>boja</ets> neck collar, fetter.
Cf. <er>Buoy</er>.]</ety> <def>A double slip of leather by which bells
are fastened to a hawk's legs.</def>⟦br⟧
